(3379, 3858, '_themify_builder_settings', 's:4779:"a:3:{i:0;a:2:{s:9:"row_order";s:1:"0";s:4:"cols";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:10:"grid_class";s:19:"col-full first last";s:7:"modules";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:8:"mod_name";s:4:"text";s:12:"mod_settings";a:1:{s:12:"content_text";s:178:"<h4>True drag & drop content builder that lets you build any page layouts with live frontend preview.<br />What you see is what you get. Works on desktop, tablet and mobile.</h4>";}}}}}}i:1;a:2:{s:9:"row_order";s:1:"1";s:4:"cols";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:10:"grid_class";s:19:"col-full first last";s:7:"modules";a:3:{i:0;a:2:{s:8:"mod_name";s:5:"image";s:12:"mod_settings";a:8:{s:11:"style_image";s:11:"image-right";s:9:"url_image";s:72:"http://themify.me/demo/themes/builder/files/2013/06/feature-settings.jpg";s:16:"appearance_image";s:7:"rounded";s:11:"width_image";s:3:"415";s:12:"height_image";s:3:"259";s:11:"title_image";s:13:"Themify Panel";s:13:"caption_image";s:391:"<h4>If we build a feature in the theme, we\'ll build the options as well.</h4>\n<p>Along with the standard settings (favicon, logo image, header code, footer code, search & feed setting, etc.), each theme has its unique features which you can configure via the Settings tab. For example, if the theme has a feature box slideshow, you will have options to choose how the slideshow displays.</p>";s:9:"css_image";s:12:"feature-item";}}i:1;a:2:{s:8:"mod_name";s:5:"image";s:12:"mod_settings";a:7:{s:11:"style_image";s:10:"image-left";s:9:"url_image";s:69:"http://themify.me/demo/themes/builder/files/2013/06/feature-skins.jpg";s:11:"width_image";s:3:"415";s:12:"height_image";s:3:"263";s:11:"title_image";s:5:"Skins";s:13:"caption_image";s:384:"<h4>All themes come with at least one skin. Skins provide different looks for your theme without changing the core functionality.</h4>\n<p>Skins can be swapped in & out under the Skins tab. All skins come with a preview image similar to WordPress themes. You can also create custom skins: simply drop in a folder with the style.css and a screenshot and your skin will be available.</p>";s:9:"css_image";s:12:"feature-item";}}i:2;a:2:{s:8:"mod_name";s:5:"image";s:12:"mod_settings";a:8:{s:11:"style_image";s:11:"image-right";s:9:"url_image";s:77:"http://themify.me/demo/themes/builder/files/2013/06/feature-import-export.png";s:16:"appearance_image";s:7:"rounded";s:11:"width_image";s:3:"415";s:12:"height_image";s:3:"213";s:11:"title_image";s:15:"Import & Export";s:13:"caption_image";s:295:"<h4>Importing & Exporting has never been this easy, seriously.</h4>\n<p>Everything\'s been taken care of. With our data structure in place you can make fast & clean backups of your settings easily. Export will generate a downloadable file of all your settings which you can import at any time.</p>";s:9:"css_image";s:12:"feature-item";}}}}}}i:2;a:2:{s:9:"row_order";s:1:"2";s:4:"cols";a:4:{i:0;a:2:{s:10:"grid_class";s:12:"col4-1 first";s:7:"modules";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:8:"mod_name";s:5:"image";s:12:"mod_settings";a:7:{s:11:"style_image";s:9:"image-top";s:9:"url_image";s:76:"http://themify.me/demo/themes/builder/files/2013/06/feature-easy-styling.jpg";s:16:"appearance_image";s:7:"rounded";s:11:"width_image";s:3:"222";s:12:"height_image";s:3:"140";s:11:"title_image";s:13:"Styling Panel";s:13:"caption_image";s:57:"Just click & select, and we\'ll do the CSS coding for you.";}}}}i:1;a:2:{s:10:"grid_class";s:6:"col4-1";s:7:"modules";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:8:"mod_name";s:5:"image";s:12:"mod_settings";a:7:{s:11:"style_image";s:9:"image-top";s:9:"url_image";s:76:"http://themify.me/demo/themes/builder/files/2013/06/feature-color-picker.jpg";s:16:"appearance_image";s:7:"rounded";s:11:"width_image";s:3:"222";s:12:"height_image";s:3:"140";s:11:"title_image";s:12:"Color Picker";s:13:"caption_image";s:76:"With the live color picker, you don\'t need to know any HTML hex color codes.";}}}}i:2;a:2:{s:10:"grid_class";s:6:"col4-1";s:7:"modules";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:8:"mod_name";s:5:"image";s:12:"mod_settings";a:7:{s:11:"style_image";s:9:"image-top";s:9:"url_image";s:75:"http://themify.me/demo/themes/builder/files/2013/06/feature-img-library.jpg";s:16:"appearance_image";s:7:"rounded";s:11:"width_image";s:3:"222";s:12:"height_image";s:3:"140";s:11:"title_image";s:13:"Image Preview";s:13:"caption_image";s:74:"The background images you uploaded are stored in the library with preview.";}}}}i:3;a:2:{s:10:"grid_class";s:11:"col4-1 last";s:7:"modules";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:8:"mod_name";s:5:"image";s:12:"mod_settings";a:7:{s:11:"style_image";s:9:"image-top";s:9:"url_image";s:69:"http://themify.me/demo/themes/builder/files/2013/06/feature-reset.jpg";s:16:"appearance_image";s:7:"rounded";s:11:"width_image";s:3:"222";s:12:"height_image";s:3:"140";s:11:"title_image";s:14:"Reset Settings";s:13:"caption_image";s:63:"Made a huge mess? No problem. Reset it and start over again. :)";}}}}}}}";'),
